<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-offset-3 col-md-6">

      <h1>
        welcome to <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-book"></span><strong>Bookers</strong>  !!
      </h1>
      <p>In <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-book"></span><strong>Bookers</strong>,<br>
        you can share and exchange your opinions , inpressions , and emotions<br>
